body.value: linear-gradient( to left, transparent var(--size-4-6), black var(--size-4-6) )
ui-sans-serif, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Inter", "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", sans-serif
ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, "Cascadia Mono", "Roboto Mono", "DejaVu Sans Mono", "Liberation Mono", Menlo, Monaco, "Consolas", "Source Code Pro", monospace

[dir=\"ltr\"].value: linear-gradient( to right, transparent var(--size-4-6), black var(--size-4-6) )

.workspace-split.mod-root > .workspace-l.value: background-color 200ms ease-in-out, border-color 200ms ease-in-out, opacity 200ms ease-in-out

input[type=\"color\"].value: box-shadow 0.15s ease-in-out, outline 0.15s ease-in-out, border 0.15s ease-in-out, opacity 0.15s ease-in-out
transform 0.15s ease-in-out, width 0.1s ease-in-out, left 0.1s ease-in-out

.tooltip .tooltip-arrow.value: drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px var(--color-base-60)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4))
drop-shadow(0px 0px 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)) drop-shadow(0px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3)) drop-shadow(0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3))

textarea.webviewer-adblock-lists.value: linear-gradient( to left, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) var(--size-4-4), #000000 var(--size-4-8) )
